{"tid":2334434,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"啲窮人食嘢真係好麻煩","createTime":"2020-12-21T07:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T07:27:15.000Z","uid":330057,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e1e1af87229657cebb2a9c21acf5c932a6c70dc","tid":2334434,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"餐廳加少少價就嘈三嘈四<br />\n加幾蚊雞都話嫌貴，走去第二間狗屎垃圾食味精餐<br />\n又唔諗吓人地經營有幾辛苦，知唔知人哋搞手都係想打個和？<br />\n人哋有錢人食嘢下下都幾千蚊都幾皮都有<br />\n唔通餐廳次次加價幾舊水又同你講咩<br />\n又唔見人哋嫌貴<br />\n所以服務啲窮人真係麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bc69464fa7ce98982d1dcb0e552e9252c9a981","tid":2334434,"uid":330057,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"窮人就唔好學人食嘢<br />\n食少幾次野儲啲錢<br />\n買層樓仲好過啦<br />\n廢青"},{"pid":"ffe08a333836c95f6195eb8287042804c8c2cb66","tid":2334434,"uid":22891,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:24:20.000Z","msg":"窮人思想: 嚴以待人，寬以律己"},{"pid":"7625443d550627a915cadebd423bdc252b532404","tid":2334434,"uid":330057,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffe08a333836c95f6195eb8287042804c8c2cb66","tid":2334434,"uid":22891,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:24:20.000Z","msg":"窮人思想: 嚴以待人，寬以律己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"為咗個幾蚊雞走去食啲味精垃圾<br />\n就連好少少嘅餐廳都留唔住<br />\n最後全部就大家鬥平整味精狗飯<br />\n所以窮人食垃圾真係抵撚死<br />\n根本就自己攞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b72bb6cee323165a7f061d4bf5b1ece839f294","tid":2334434,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"仲要食野雜雜聲 正一死雜種"},{"pid":"58aae32dcd87fc377d7a2eae5e7fbbe2e5676f92","tid":2334434,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"36b72bb6cee323165a7f061d4bf5b1ece839f294","tid":2334434,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"仲要食野雜雜聲 正一死雜種"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"飲嘢飲到底嘅時候有啲珠珠聲<br />\n狼吞虎嚥 餓狗搶屎咁嘅聲<br />\n可能趕住下1秒返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}